---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <!-- Title -->
          <h1 class="title">About Me</h1>
          <h2 class="subtitle">Get to know me a little better</h2>
          
          <!-- Profile Image -->
          <div class="columns is-centered">
            <div class="column is-one-third has-text-centered">
              <figure class="image is-128x128 is-inline-block">
                <img class="is-rounded" src="/images/me.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
              </figure>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <div class="content">
            <p>
              Hello! I'm Emil Schütt, a passionate student in Cybersecurity with a strong background in programming and a deep interest in data security.
              I am currently pursuing my Master of Science in Engineering with a specialization in Computer Security at Blekinge Institute of Technology.
              In my free time, I love working on projects that involve programming, networking technologies, and experimenting with different frameworks.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Skills Section -->
          <h3 class="title is-4">Skills</h3>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Programming Languages:</strong> Rust, C++, Python, C#, Java</li>
                <li><strong>Tools & Technologies:</strong> Docker, Git, ASP.Net, React</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Operating Systems:</strong> Ubuntu, Fedora, Windows</li>
                <li><strong>Other Skills:</strong> Networking, Cryptography, Technical Troubleshooting</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Experience Section -->
          <h3 class="title is-4">Experience</h3>
          <div class="content">
            <p>
              I have worked on various projects ranging from network security tools to web development using frameworks like React and ASP.Net.
              I’ve also been involved in teaching programming and technical troubleshooting, helping others to understand and resolve complex technical issues.
              My latest focus is on Rust development, where I’ve been working on projects like RTMP protocol implementation and cryptographic libraries.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contact Section -->
          <h3 class="title is-4">Contact</h3>
          <div class="content">
            <p>
              Feel free to check out my work on 
              <a href="https://github.com/retrokiller543" target="_blank">GitHub</a> and 
              <a href="https://gitlab.com/retrokiller543" target="_blank">GitLab</a>. 
              You can also reach out to me via email, LinkedIn, or GitLab. 
              I'm always open to discussing new opportunities, collaborations, or just having a chat about technology, programming, and cybersecurity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
    section.section {
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    figure.image {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
</style>